oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Carl Peters Job No. 37419
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Sovine, Red; Duke of Paducah, 1901-1986; Smiley, Dolores;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1967) for an order placed by Carl Peters for 200 two color jumbos for a performance by Red Sovine, Duke of Paducah, Delores Smiley, and more at Central High School on November 12. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
